                        <seg type="rubrication">Nomina sacra; names of the donors; groups of lines
                           (alternating with black lines) on the incipit pages of Texts I and III;
                           two initial lines of the incipit of Text II; two initial lines of
                           sections of Texts I-2 and I-3; some words in Text II; the words salām
                           “salutation” and sǝbḥat “glory” in Text II; elements of the punctuation
                           signs; elements of Ethiopic numerals.</seg>
                     </handNote>
